(5, 'John W.', '\"This platform made getting a home repair so easy. The plumber who came to fix our leaking sink was prompt, professional, and cleaned up after the job. I will definitely use them again.\"', 5, 1, '2024-11-11 12:17:37', '2024-11-11 12:17:37'),
(6, 'Maria G.', '\"Wonderful experience from start to finish. The cleaning service exceeded my expectations. My home looks spotless, and the booking process was super convenient. 10/10!\"', 5, 1, '2024-11-11 12:18:25', '2024-11-11 12:18:25');
